general_perception.description and explanation: In the traffic image, there is a dark-colored sedan car partially visible, parked on the right side of the road facing the direction of the ego car. Although the car is not moving, it occupies part of the road and narrows the driving path for the ego car.

1.description and explanation: This is a parked car detected in a night scene. The car appears to be stationary on the side of the road, partially lit by the nearby streetlights. Since it is parked, it directly influences the driving behavior of the ego car by requiring careful navigation to safely pass without colliding, maintaining an adequate distance to avoid any unforeseen movements from the parked car, such as a door opening or the car pulling back onto the road. The presence of this parked car also reduces the available road width, necessitating reduced speed and increased alertness especially in a low-light environment.

driving_suggestion: Proceed with caution, maintain a lower speed due to wet road conditions, and be prepared to stop or maneuver if the parked car obstructs the path. Utilize headlights and pay close attention to any other road users that may be less visible at night.
